## 7. Quick Reference: Libraries Already Available

| Library | Available In | Use For |
|---|---|---|
| `framer-motion` | `Hero.tsx`, `Contact.tsx` | `useScroll`, `useTransform`, `useSpring`, mouse-tracking parallax |
| `gsap` + `ScrollTrigger` | `Who.tsx`, `WhyInfotainmentWorks.tsx`, `ProblemsSection.tsx` | Scrub-based scroll parallax, pinned section internal parallax |

> [!TIP]
> For new parallax sections (Contact, Footer), **prefer Framer Motion** to keep GSAP context isolated to the pins. GSAP contexts crossing component boundaries were the root cause of previous jitter bugs.
